Class LeafNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.planning.queryplan.PlanNode
      • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.planning.queryplan.LeafNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FilterAndProjectEdgesNode, FilterAndProjectVerticesNode

    public abstract class LeafNode
extends PlanNode
    Represents a leaf node in the query plan. Leaf nodes are different in terms of their input which is a data set containing elements, i.e. Vertex or Edge.
